His father was a human and his mother was an Orc. He rejected his human side and Joined his villages militia or army (whatever they had) but during the war ended up fleeing. He seeks redemption from his God by destroying his foes after being a coward. Unknown to him, he has a half-elf brother named Eli who is in his adventuring party. His father was kind of a crazy whore. Bob also once tried to have relations with a dragon.